In [41]:
def norm_plot(model, grid):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 3))
    plt.title('   ({})'.format(grid))
    plt.xlabel('')
    plt.yscale('log')
    plt.plot(model.ts, model.df_additional.iloc[:, 0])
    plt.show()

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 7))
plt.title('    ')
plt.xlim([-0.05, 1])
plt.xlabel('$r$')
plt.plot([0, 0], [0, 1], '--', color='black', label='_nolegend_')
plt.plot([0, 5], [1, 1], '--', color='black', label='_nolegend_')
plt.plot(model_cyl_200.xs, model_cyl_200.phi_at_t(5))
plt.plot(model_cyl_400.xs, model_cyl_400.phi_at_t(5))
plt.plot(model_cyl_800.xs, model_cyl_800.phi_at_t(5))
plt.plot(model_cyl_1600.xs, model_cyl_1600.phi_at_t(4))
plt.plot(model_cyl_200_log.xs, model_cyl_200_log.phi_at_t(5))
plt.plot(model_cyl_400_log.xs, model_cyl_400_log.phi_at_t(4))
plt.plot(model_cyl_800_log.xs, model_cyl_800_log.phi_at_t(3))
plt.legend(['$n_x = 200$', '$n_x = 400$', '$n_x = 800$', '$n_x = 1600$', '$n_x = 200$, log',
           '$n_x = 400$, log', '$n_x = 800$, log'])
plt.show()
